      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Follow this procedure to switch cullet water pumps:</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To switch cullet water pumps:</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Go to the PVAG control panel located in the basement near the slant plate
                     clarifier.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Click on <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Settings</uicontrol>.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Click on <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">FP pumps settings</uicontrol> or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">
                        <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">RP pumps
                           settings</uicontrol>
                     </b>.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Click on <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Change pumps now</uicontrol>.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">One dirty pit pump and one clean pit pump should run during normal
                     operation.</li>
               </ul>
               <note type="note" id="note_ofl_krd_5cc" class="- topic/note ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Pumps should be in Automatic mode with automatic switchover enabled during
